{"tid":2138350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會加入制裁? 批中國開放走回頭路 瑞士外長開砲：西方各國將果斷回應","createTime":"2020-08-03T13:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T02:17:10.000Z","uid":291835,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e61e049427358841c8073aaeb24d9f15710f28a","tid":2138350,"uid":291835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3248403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3248403&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=1c924bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3248403&h=f928db51\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3248403</a><br />\n〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕中國政府排除異己、打壓人權之舉，引起歐美國家皺眉。《法新社》2日報導，瑞士外交部長凱西斯（Ignazio Cassis）受訪時表示，中國的開放之路愈走愈回去，若中方依然故我，西方各國將更加果斷地做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，凱西斯向瑞士週報《星期展望》（SonntagsBlick）表示，中國的政治自由化未能趕上經濟自由化，且中國侵犯人權的事件與日俱增，「我們看到中國正在背離開放之路」，這意味瑞士必須更堅定地捍衞自身利益和價值，將藉由加強國際法和多邊體系達成此目標。<br />\n<br />\n凱西斯表示，瑞士和中國建交70年來，一直與北京建立「有建設性、且不乏批判性」的關係，法治和人權一直是雙方對話的一環。然而，他坦言，瑞士現在了解到，中國的情況比想像中更加動盪不安，人權侵犯事件持續增加，而瑞士希望保護這些權益。<br />\n<br />\n在談及香港國安法時，凱西斯直言該法是從根本上加強控制香港，並警告中國若摒棄「一國兩制」原則，將影響很多在香港投資的瑞士企業，「若中國堅持新路線，西方世界將更果斷地回應。」"},{"pid":"73d95d7fa36df979b47a02c681e7c3140e3bd682","tid":2138350,"uid":291835,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:53:23.000Z","msg":"對抗人類文明既威脅, 無得再中立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b949fd8144c7eb7aa8ffe9e4d31d1fc92ef59c","tid":2138350,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6699009e8f4362daa88f03bc6d75662d0e8d6a54","tid":2138350,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea601fbd8bac7197e4d66fba0012b4eb3ab17dba","tid":2138350,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"實際行動緊要D"},{"pid":"95fa32b11c705b14b130006e9b040d3cd1700df4","tid":2138350,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"瑞士唔係中立國嚟既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687f9e6628e16d231dff29caf436376bf910dfa0","tid":2138350,"uid":291835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fa32b11c705b14b130006e9b040d3cd1700df4","tid":2138350,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"瑞士唔係中立國嚟既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"所以值得重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e29a8c463ca829047877cf39775cd1d3f4fa287","tid":2138350,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"瑞士知道中共再唔收手就會打扙，應該會影響到瑞士"},{"pid":"91071eac576609bf4e625c803cc9527c4ce5de96","tid":2138350,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"CUT曬D中国戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd8a319597adb4993e90d8d299fb392ebec76d9","tid":2138350,"uid":26218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"強國好多資產係瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50273c3d178c4ce3a55bbf07668eafa2e219d79f","tid":2138350,"uid":291835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"查返資料, 瑞士竟然係2019年4月簽左一戴一露備忘錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ab9e1aae54b3f1ba167b8dd2a31821a73dfed6"